title: Borgia Season 1 1080p H265 AC3 5.1 EN SRT
description:
This is the entire season one of Borgia (not to be confused with "The Borgias"), here uploaded as h265 videos which gives fantastic quality for a modest file size.

Taken from the Bluray raw upload, and encoded as h256 (or HEVC) full HD 1920x1080p at 23.976fps at 3000kbps with 5.1 AC3 audio encoded at 384kbps.

The English subtitles are included in the mkvs (not hardcoded).

The subtitle SRT files also included.

Enjoy, and please, please, continue to seed after you have downloaded
